---
// HowToParticipate.astro
---
<section id="como-participar" class="relative pb-24 px-6 md:px-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#f6f7fa]">
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-start">
    <div class="text-left mb-16 space-y-4 max-w-2xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-pink-600 font-syne font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">
        <span>Fácil y Rápido</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-syne font-bold text-gray-900 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        ¿Cómo Participar?
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards container -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 md:gap-8 w-full">
      
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(236,72,153,0.15)] text-center">
        <!-- Number Badge -->
        <span class="absolute -top-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-pink-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-syne shadow-lg rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
          1
        </span>
        
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mt-6 mb-6 p-5 rounded-full shadow-inner ring-1 ring-pink-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-pink-600"><path d="M15 5.5v13"/><path d="M9 5.5v13"/><rect width="18" height="14" x="3" y="5" rx="2" ry="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-syne font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Elige tu número</h3>
        <p class="font-work-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Selecciona tu número. Date prisa antes de que alguien más escoja el que tienes en mente y escríbenos!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(236,72,153,0.15)] text-center mt-0 md:mt-8">
        <!-- Number Badge -->
        <span class="absolute -top-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-pink-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-syne shadow-lg -rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
          2
        </span>
        
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mt-6 mb-6 p-5 rounded-full shadow-inner ring-1 ring-pink-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-pink-600"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"/><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-syne font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Realiza tu pago o abono</h3>
        <p class="font-work-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Realiza tu primer pago o abono únicamente a nuestra cuenta de <span class="font-semibold text-blue-900">Bancolombia.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(236,72,153,0.15)] text-center mt-0 md:mt-16">
        <!-- Number Badge -->
        <span class="absolute -top-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-pink-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-syne shadow-lg rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
          3
        </span>
        
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="mt-6 mb-6 p-5 rounded-full shadow-inner ring-1 ring-pink-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-pink-600"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="m9 15 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-syne font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Recibe tu recibo</h3>
        <p class="font-work-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Recibirás de inmediato tu comprobante digital oficial de la rifa. Ya estarás listo para jugar con total transparencia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
